Placed an order from the Netherlands and the package was delivered in good order. Also a good customer service. Professional and fast delivery.
Recently placed an order with Shun Dat for delivery to Toronto, Canada. Owner was very responsive and helpful. Received my order within a week in perfect condition.
Mr Koo is familiar with the products and is able to provide good advice. Delivery was smooth too. Great place to get Malaysian 道地土产

I had an exceptional experience with this shop, a place offering a wide range of Malaysia's local food products. The selection was impressive and authentic. The products evoking memories of my travels in Malaysia, and the customer service was exceptionally good. Overall, I highly recommend this shop for anyone seeking for Malaysia local products. I look forward to returning for more of their delightful offerings.
